BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:f-wgOoWTxnsEQEDsJtGRs
SUMMARY:29th Annual Daffodil Day
DTSTAMP:20260317T050001Z
DTSTART:20260320T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Friday\, March 20\, 2026 11:00am – 2:00pm (or until supplies la
	st) Celebrate the First Day of Spring at Pike Place Market’s 29th Annual D
	affodil Day! Nothing says "spring has arrived" quite like the cheerful blo
	om of daffodils! Celebrate the changing of the seasons at Pike Place Marke
	t during the 29th Annual Daffodil Day on Friday\, March 20. Stop by the Ma
	rket’s famous Clock & Sign to pick up a free bundle of fresh\, fragrant da
	ffodils and learn more about the dedicated local flower farmers who grew t
	hem. These beautiful blooms\, in vibrant shades of yellow\, white\, and or
	ange\, are a sure sign that sunnier days are ahead! Don't miss live busker
	 music on the Farm Truck to celebrate the occasion\, and be sure to stop b
	y the PIKE BOX tent as we kick off registration for the upcoming CSA seaso
	n. Make a day of it by strolling through the Market’s historic arcade\, gr
	abbing a bite to eat\, or picking up a unique\, locally made gift. Enjoy t
	he sights\, sounds\, and flavors of Pike Place Market. All the \n\nhttps:/
	/www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/29th-daffodil-day/?occurrence=202
	6-03-20\n\nFrom Pike Place Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/29th-daffodil-day/?occu
	rrence=2026-03-20
LOCATION:Pike Place Market\, 85 Pike Street
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
